verbose_text: In vitro kinase assays demonstrated that piceatannol significantly inhibited phosphatidylinositol 3-kinase (PI3K) activity and suppressed phosphatidylinositol -trisphosphate (PIP 3) expression in the H-ras MCF10A cells.
